        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of any neuro- or psycho-active medications that alters balance;

          -  any other neurological conditions or sensory disorders affecting postural control;
             such as brain tumor, or substance abuse; orthopedic diseases;

          -  ongoing/recent (within 3 months) balance rehabilitation.
